@deviceToken =

### 终端列表（分页 + 筛选）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/terminals?page=1&page_size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 终端列表（按SN筛选）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/terminals?page=1&page_size=10&sn=TERM-001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 终端列表（按状态筛选: offline / online / disabled）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/terminals?page=1&page_size=10&status=offline
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 终端列表（按门店筛选）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/terminals?page=1&page_size=10&store_id=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 获取终端详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/terminals/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 创建终端
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/terminals
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sn": "TERM-001",
  "name": "收银终端A1",
  "type": "pos",
  "store_id": 1
}

### 更新终端
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/terminals/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "收银终端A1-升级版",
  "type": "pos_v2",
  "store_id": 1,
  "status": "offline"
}

### 删除终端
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/terminals/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================================
### 终端设备接口（独立认证，使用 X-Device-Token）
### ============================================================

### 终端心跳上报
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/terminals/TERM-001/heartbeat
X-Device-Token: {{deviceToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ip_address": "192.168.1.100",
  "mac_address": "AA:BB:CC:DD:EE:FF"
}

### 终端轮换设备令牌
# 成功后将返回的 device_token 填到上方 @deviceToken 变量中
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/terminals/TERM-001/rotate-token
X-Device-Token: {{deviceToken}}
